Want to install the app on your Blackberry? It works on devices with OS 5.0 and higher. First though, you need to install the MintChip API.
<br /><br />
Open BlackBerry Desktop Software and click on 'Applications':
<br />
<img src="img\Applications.png" />
<br /><br />
In the top right hand corner, click on 'Import Files' and select MintChipBlackBerryApi.alx
<br /><br />
<img src="img\MintChipBlackberryApi.png" />
<br />
<br />
Make sure to select MintChip API, then in the bottom right hand corner, click on 'Apply'
<br />
<br />
<img src="img\Apply.png" />
<br />
<br />
<img src="img\Update.png" />
<br /><br />
After everything is installed, now you can install Bill Splittr.
